1
00:00:19,162 --> 00:00:24,349
♪The whole world is lit up♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,661
♪Because you exist♪

3
00:00:25,662 --> 00:00:27,741
♪You're always♪

4
00:00:27,742 --> 00:00:32,391
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

5
00:00:32,392 --> 00:00:35,124
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

6
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,691
♪Hold tight♪

7
00:00:36,692 --> 00:00:42,481
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

8
00:00:42,482 --> 00:00:48,132
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 21=

9
00:00:52,540 --> 00:00:54,298
Right now, the public is talking

10
00:00:54,299 --> 00:00:55,780
a lot about Mu Group.

11
00:00:55,900 --> 00:00:58,180
They say
the internal structure is a mess.

12
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:00,139
And that the current heir

13
00:01:00,140 --> 00:01:02,019
is a complete amateur
in the auction world

14
00:01:02,460 --> 00:01:04,539
and can't handle
the group's responsibilities.

15
00:01:05,325 --> 00:01:07,440
(Moser International)
Even the partners we previously

16
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,280
negotiated with
want to cancel their contracts.

17
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,299
What do you plan to do?

18
00:01:15,940 --> 00:01:16,780
Don't worry.

19
00:01:16,859 --> 00:01:18,819
I will definitely
give the board an explanation.

20
00:01:19,259 --> 00:01:20,700
I won't let these public opinions

21
00:01:20,859 --> 00:01:22,539
continue to affect Mu Group.

22
00:01:28,219 --> 00:01:29,498
He Min, why are you here?

23
00:01:29,499 --> 00:01:30,220
Yu,

24
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:32,340
will you come with me?

25
00:01:32,460 --> 00:01:33,860
Let's go get married right now.

26
00:01:34,139 --> 00:01:36,379
I can give you
the grandest wedding possible

27
00:01:36,460 --> 00:01:38,459
and make you
the young mistress of the He Group.

28
00:01:38,619 --> 00:01:39,939
That way, you won't have to worry

29
00:01:39,940 --> 00:01:41,860
about being mistreated
after leaving the Mu family.

30
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,500
I can help you.

31
00:01:50,259 --> 00:01:51,260
He Min,

32
00:01:51,660 --> 00:01:53,140
I won't marry you.

33
00:01:54,059 --> 00:01:55,780
Even if I have nothing now,

34
00:01:56,059 --> 00:01:56,819
I can't use you

35
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:58,338
to achieve what I want to do.

36
00:01:58,339 --> 00:02:00,379
Are you together with that Shen Jibai?

37
00:02:01,979 --> 00:02:05,258
Are you going to marry him
to become the mistress of the Mu family

38
00:02:05,259 --> 00:02:06,539
and stay with them?

39
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:12,180
He Min,

40
00:02:12,980 --> 00:02:14,538
when I asked you to help me act before,

41
00:02:14,539 --> 00:02:16,580
I already made things very clear.

42
00:02:17,059 --> 00:02:18,859
I consider you my best friend.

43
00:02:19,539 --> 00:02:20,859
Since I returned to the country,

44
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:22,780
I'm very grateful
that you've helped me so much.

45
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:24,580
But

46
00:02:25,140 --> 00:02:26,859
there can't be anything more between us.

47
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:28,020
Why?

48
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,859
Right now, rumors
about Mu Group are everywhere,

49
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:32,220
and the stock price is plummeting.

50
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:33,658
Why do you want to stay

51
00:02:33,659 --> 00:02:35,259
with a family that abandoned you?

52
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:38,220
I can help you.

53
00:02:38,779 --> 00:02:40,459
Take advantage of the crisis.

54
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,818
In your capacity as a director,

55
00:02:41,819 --> 00:02:43,180
join He Group.

56
00:02:43,619 --> 00:02:45,699
We'll handle
next quarter's auction together

57
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:47,340
and acquire Mu Group.

58
00:02:48,020 --> 00:02:50,500
You might even be able to win
your dream Golden Hammer Award.

59
00:02:52,700 --> 00:02:55,259
Even if I'm not
the daughter of the Mu family anymore,

60
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:58,979
that doesn't mean I should kick
Mu Group while it's down, right?

61
00:02:58,980 --> 00:03:01,379
Are you unwilling to hurt Mu Group,

62
00:03:01,619 --> 00:03:04,099
or are you unwilling to hurt Shen Jibai?

63
00:03:04,379 --> 00:03:06,419
Everyone is saying

64
00:03:06,980 --> 00:03:07,899
that he's an amateur

65
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:09,699
who can't manage the company at all.

66
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:11,460
Mu Group will go
bankrupt sooner or later.

67
00:03:12,180 --> 00:03:14,539
Are you sure you want
to be with someone like that?

68
00:03:15,339 --> 00:03:17,220
My relationship with Shen Jibai

69
00:03:17,420 --> 00:03:19,020
doesn't need to be explained to you.

70
00:03:20,539 --> 00:03:21,939
And I want to tell you,

71
00:03:23,099 --> 00:03:26,259
Mu Group is my mother's
and grandfather's legacy.

72
00:03:26,260 --> 00:03:27,538
It doesn't belong to Xu Mingzhu.

73
00:03:27,539 --> 00:03:29,180
It doesn't belong to Shen Jibai either.

74
00:03:31,219 --> 00:03:32,859
I will do what I need to do

75
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:35,139
to protect what I should protect.

76
00:03:44,339 --> 00:03:47,220
Why did you let
these forgeries stay on the market?

77
00:03:47,659 --> 00:03:49,299
You even used them to manufacture news

78
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:51,300
to make Mu Group's stock price crash.

79
00:03:52,339 --> 00:03:53,900
If this continues,

80
00:03:54,219 --> 00:03:56,300
who would still work with Mu Group?

81
00:03:56,460 --> 00:03:58,300
What do you gain from doing this?

82
00:04:00,659 --> 00:04:02,379
If I can't have it,

83
00:04:03,180 --> 00:04:04,979
no one else can.

84
00:04:05,762 --> 00:04:08,202
Mu Chenzhou didn't want
to leave me an inheritance,

85
00:04:09,499 --> 00:04:11,979
nor did he want
to give me any company shares.

86
00:04:12,619 --> 00:04:14,979
What did I mean to him all these years?

87
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:17,580
If you hadn't had
that evil thought back then

88
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:19,580
to swap Zhiyu and me,

89
00:04:21,179 --> 00:04:23,720
how could you have
become the mistress of Mu Group

90
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,738
and enjoyed everything you have now?

91
00:04:26,739 --> 00:04:28,260
Don't you think it's enough?

92
00:04:33,900 --> 00:04:35,340
Of course not.

93
00:04:36,339 --> 00:04:37,659
All these years,

94
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:38,899
I gave my heart and soul

95
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:39,939
to Mu Chenzhou.

96
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:41,700
Why should I end up with nothing?

97
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:43,700
Because you've done nothing but evil.

98
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:46,059
If it weren't for you,

99
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:48,020
my mother
wouldn't have died of depression.

100
00:04:48,299 --> 00:04:49,699
You deserve all of this.

101
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:51,859
You're a fake!
What right do you have to judge me?

102
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,619
If it weren't for me,

103
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:58,419
how could you have
become the daughter of the Mu family?

104
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:03,658
You've enjoyed
your status as the heiress for years.

105
00:05:03,659 --> 00:05:05,659
You should be thanking me.

106
00:05:13,339 --> 00:05:14,220
What?

107
00:05:15,219 --> 00:05:16,619
You want to hit me?

108
00:05:17,620 --> 00:05:18,859
Don't forget,

109
00:05:19,539 --> 00:05:20,699
both your lives

110
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:22,739
were in my hands once.

111
00:05:24,060 --> 00:05:25,700
Don't push me too far,

112
00:05:26,219 --> 00:05:27,979
or there's nothing I won't do.

113
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:42,659
Of course, I wouldn't actually hit you.

114
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:45,020
After all,

115
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:47,739
you were once my father's mistress.

116
00:05:48,419 --> 00:05:50,580
But now that Mu Chenzhou is dead,

117
00:05:51,219 --> 00:05:52,859
and you didn't get
any inheritance rights,

118
00:05:53,659 --> 00:05:55,580
isn't it time for you
to leave the Mu family?

119
00:05:56,539 --> 00:05:58,340
Just you wait.

120
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:21,419
Mr. Mu.

121
00:06:22,179 --> 00:06:22,940
Look over here.

122
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:23,499
Mr. Shen,

123
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:25,519
regarding the public opinion
that you are an outsider

124
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:27,919
who lacks the ability to lead
the Mu Group, how will you respond?

125
00:06:27,919 --> 00:06:29,579
What is the Mu Group's next plan?

126
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:30,819
Could you give us a response?

127
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:31,658
Yes.

128
00:06:31,659 --> 00:06:32,699
Regarding auctions,

129
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:34,299
I am indeed an outsider.

130
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:37,139
But my fiancée,

131
00:06:37,140 --> 00:06:38,099
Mu Zhiyu,

132
00:06:38,219 --> 00:06:40,380
is a top international auctioneer.

133
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:41,738
Soon,

134
00:06:41,739 --> 00:06:43,220
we will announce our marriage.

135
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:44,900
In the future,

136
00:06:45,099 --> 00:06:47,099
she will not only be
the lady of the Mu Group

137
00:06:47,179 --> 00:06:49,380
but also our General Manager.

138
00:06:50,099 --> 00:06:50,900
This

139
00:06:50,979 --> 00:06:52,220
is the source of my confidence.

140
00:06:54,060 --> 00:06:54,939
Really?

141
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:55,739
Congratulations!

142
00:06:59,979 --> 00:07:00,899
They

143
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:02,299
have no shame.

144
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:05,539
They were messing around
right under my nose before,

145
00:07:06,060 --> 00:07:08,820
and now they're openly
announcing their marriage.

146
00:07:13,659 --> 00:07:15,539
Don't be angry, Mr. He.

147
00:07:15,779 --> 00:07:16,900
That's why

148
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:20,020
we can't let them get too smug.

149
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:22,220
We must speed up our actions.

150
00:07:22,339 --> 00:07:23,900
I won't let them have their way.

151
00:07:26,299 --> 00:07:27,858
In the last quarter of this year,

152
00:07:27,859 --> 00:07:29,859
the Mu Group will hold a new auction.

153
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:31,418
If Shen Jibai and Mu Zhiyu

154
00:07:31,419 --> 00:07:33,538
turn the tables at this auction,

155
00:07:33,539 --> 00:07:34,418
then the Mu Group

156
00:07:34,419 --> 00:07:35,619
will not only avoid collapse

157
00:07:35,620 --> 00:07:38,380
but might even break into
the top three auction houses globally.

158
00:07:38,859 --> 00:07:40,899
When that time comes, your He family

159
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:42,460
will be in for it.

160
00:07:43,219 --> 00:07:44,419
Don't worry about that.

161
00:07:44,739 --> 00:07:45,900
I already have a plan.

162
00:07:46,099 --> 00:07:49,460
Hong's "Changing Mountains and Rivers"
is a popular exhibit at home and abroad.

163
00:07:50,260 --> 00:07:51,858
If He Group

164
00:07:51,859 --> 00:07:54,499
can cooperate with Hong to secure
"Changing Mountains and Rivers,"

165
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:56,659
we'll be stealing
the Mu Group's spotlight.

166
00:07:56,979 --> 00:07:58,139
Then, it will be difficult

167
00:07:58,140 --> 00:07:59,940
for them to make a comeback.

168
00:08:00,659 --> 00:08:02,020
That's a good idea.

169
00:08:02,419 --> 00:08:04,619
But I heard
that Hong has a strange temper.

170
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:07,580
Mu Zhiyu went many times
before she finally got a partnership.

171
00:08:11,539 --> 00:08:12,659
Can you handle it?

172
00:08:15,859 --> 00:08:17,059
There is one person

173
00:08:17,539 --> 00:08:18,900
who might be able to.

174
00:08:28,099 --> 00:08:29,260
Grandpa.

175
00:08:29,460 --> 00:08:31,218
(Tomb of Father, Ye Weiguo)
Mom,

176
00:08:31,219 --> 00:08:32,800
(Tomb of Mother, Ye Li)
I've come to see you.

177
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:35,340
The person
standing next to me is Shen Jibai.

178
00:08:37,179 --> 00:08:39,660
He is actually your
and Dad's biological child.

179
00:08:41,819 --> 00:08:44,418
Back then, Grandpa
started from scratch with Mom

180
00:08:44,419 --> 00:08:46,019
and founded the company.

181
00:08:46,539 --> 00:08:48,619
Later, after Mom and Dad got married,

182
00:08:49,100 --> 00:08:51,340
Grandpa handed the company
over to Dad to manage,

183
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:53,099
and it was later renamed Mu Group.

184
00:08:54,059 --> 00:08:55,859
Now that Shen Jibai is back,

185
00:08:56,362 --> 00:08:59,557
I believe he
will protect your hard work.

186
00:09:01,162 --> 00:09:02,300
It's just me...

187
00:09:03,579 --> 00:09:05,259
If you were still here,

188
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:08,019
would you still love me?

189
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:10,859
I believe
all the members of the Mu family

190
00:09:12,779 --> 00:09:14,779
will love you just as they always have.

191
00:09:14,980 --> 00:09:16,300
(Shen Jibai,)

192
00:09:17,059 --> 00:09:18,379
(thank you.)

193
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:25,899
There were many things that I didn't tell you,
fearing they would affect your mood.

194
00:09:32,179 --> 00:09:34,149
In fact, your biological mother, Shen Yi,

195
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,532
loves you very much too.

196
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:42,899
Fine.

197
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:45,700
I promise you.

198
00:09:48,699 --> 00:09:50,940
I will never go to see her again.

199
00:09:52,620 --> 00:09:54,700
I will do as you requested

200
00:09:55,659 --> 00:09:56,961
and stay far away from her.

201
00:09:56,962 --> 00:09:59,859
♪Before you boarded the flight♪

202
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:01,739
But you must promise me

203
00:10:02,939 --> 00:10:04,820
that you will take good care of her.

204
00:10:09,725 --> 00:10:12,111
♪Far behind♪

205
00:10:12,112 --> 00:10:17,759
♪The luggage in hand♪

206
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:20,979
♪Is both strange and familiar♪

207
00:10:20,980 --> 00:10:22,540
It was after meeting you

208
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:24,619
that I connected all the pieces,

209
00:10:25,140 --> 00:10:26,499
found that photo,

210
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:28,180
and finally confirmed

211
00:10:29,100 --> 00:10:31,899
that the child my mom said
she would never see again

212
00:10:31,939 --> 00:10:33,019
should be you.

213
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:36,899
It was right after that phone call

214
00:10:37,059 --> 00:10:38,460
that we moved abroad.

215
00:10:41,539 --> 00:10:42,700
Then why

216
00:10:44,220 --> 00:10:46,220
did she hand me over to Xu Mingzhu?

217
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:49,619
Xu Mingzhu forced her.

218
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:52,499
She used your life
and safety as a threat.

219
00:10:52,819 --> 00:10:54,719
To protect her own daughter,

220
00:10:54,719 --> 00:10:56,840
Shen Yi had no choice
but to go to a far-off foreign land.

221
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:01,580
I just didn't expect

222
00:11:01,939 --> 00:11:04,139
that things would later take such a turn

223
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:07,300
and end up like this.

224
00:11:09,187 --> 00:11:12,545
♪Watching you go♪

225
00:11:14,659 --> 00:11:15,820
No matter what,

226
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:19,139
we have found each other.

227
00:11:21,699 --> 00:11:22,820
In the future,

228
00:11:23,260 --> 00:11:24,700
no matter how difficult it is,

229
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:27,420
we will walk this path together.

230
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:46,430
♪Light comes beaming in♪

231
00:11:46,570 --> 00:11:50,939
♪Landing on my skin♪

232
00:11:50,940 --> 00:11:55,430
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

233
00:11:59,650 --> 00:12:03,589
♪Shadows move around♪

234
00:12:03,590 --> 00:12:08,199
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

235
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:12,730
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

236
00:12:16,330 --> 00:12:22,120
♪Don't slip away♪

237
00:12:24,570 --> 00:12:29,139
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

238
00:12:29,140 --> 00:12:33,539
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

239
00:12:33,540 --> 00:12:37,860
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

240
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:41,860
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

241
00:12:42,330 --> 00:12:46,639
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

242
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:50,969
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

243
00:12:50,970 --> 00:12:55,279
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

244
